data.description: This property is nestled in the heart of Bridgeport in a quiet peaceful neighborhood. The L shape of the house gives it a big spacious feel, this home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The living room is great for entertaining, and it accompanied by a beautiful fireplace. The master bedroom is spacious an offers a nice, secluded bathroom all to itself. The second bedroom and third bedroom both have their own big closets, the second bathroom is located in the hallway between the bedrooms and the living room. The kitchen is great for get togethers as well by offering a spacious bar top between the kitchen and dining room. This home has multiple storage closets and linin closets throughout the hallways. Following all the great inside features the back porch is nicely shaded by big mature trees and lined with a privacy fence to enjoy. This is a great property with a lot of potential as well.
